videos.description: Manu Lecomte puts Baylor up 10-8 over a Central Arkansas with a 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Lecomte left open for Baylor 3

videos.description: Mark Vital gives Tristan Clark the ball over the top as he draws the foul on the lay-up for Baylor.

videos.headline: Baylor steal leads to Clark alley-oop
